title: Oxford English Dictionary 2nd Edition - DICT format v1.1 (OED)
description:
This is the complete Oxford English Dictionary, 2nd Edition, in
compressed DICT format. It was created using the tools from <a href="
http://njw.name/oed2dict" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://njw.name/oed2dict</a>

Unlike the official CDROM version, it works on any operating system
with any dictionary program capable of reading DICT files, it is
far smaller, and it can be easily analysed by other computer
programs.

Note that this the full Oxford English Dictionary, not a concise or
abridged version. The small filesize is purely because of the
efficiency of the compressed DICT format.
